@startuml 拣货策略测试时序图

actor "JUnit" as test
participant "PickingStrategyTest" as pt
participant "NormalPicking" as normal
participant "WavePickingDecorator" as wave
participant "ColdChainPickingDecorator" as cold
participant "FragilePickingDecorator" as fragile

== 测试1: 普通拣货 ==
test -> pt: testNormalPicking()
pt -> normal: execute()
normal --> pt: "按库位顺序拣货"
pt -> pt: assertEquals ✓

== 测试2: 普通+波次+冷链 ==
test -> pt: testWaveAndColdChainPicking()
pt -> normal: new NormalPicking()
pt -> wave: new WavePickingDecorator(normal)
pt -> cold: new ColdChainPickingDecorator(wave)
pt -> cold: execute()
cold -> wave: execute()
wave -> normal: execute()
normal --> wave: "按库位顺序拣货"
wave --> cold: "...拣货 -> 波次批量拣货"
cold --> pt: "...拣货 -> 波次 -> 冷链"
pt -> pt: assertTrue(包含三项规则) ✓

== 测试3: 普通+易碎品 ==
test -> pt: testFragilePicking()
pt -> fragile: new FragilePickingDecorator(normal)
pt -> fragile: execute()
fragile -> normal: execute()
normal --> fragile: "按库位顺序拣货"
fragile --> pt: "...拣货 -> 禁止抛扔、二次复核"
pt -> pt: assertTrue ✓

== 测试4: 优先级验证 ==
test -> pt: testPriority()
pt -> cold: new ColdChainPickingDecorator(normal)
pt -> fragile: new FragilePickingDecorator(normal)
pt -> wave: new WavePickingDecorator(normal)
pt -> pt: assertTrue(5<10<20) ✓

== 测试5: 自定义优先级 ==
test -> pt: testCustomPriority()
pt -> wave: new WavePickingDecorator(normal, 1)
pt -> fragile: new FragilePickingDecorator(normal, 100)
pt -> pt: assertTrue(1 < 100) ✓

== 测试6: 多重装饰执行顺序 ==
test -> pt: testExecutionOrder()
pt -> cold: new ColdChain(wave(fragile(normal)))
pt -> cold: execute()
pt -> pt: 验证 fragileIdx < waveIdx < coldIdx ✓

@enduml
